Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.20,0:00:11.74,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,{*}Lady Pecorine{*Pecorine-sama}, you're all right!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.36,0:00:14.99,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.94,0:00:18.11,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.79,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Landosol Castle.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.79,0:00:31.49,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,We're in Landosol's Castle?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.49,0:00:34.12,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I think so, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.95,0:00:38.65,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,{\q2}But there's no one here, \Nso I'm not entirely sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.39,0:00:40.72,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,What about this portrait?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.55,0:00:44.81,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.14,0:00:48.43,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I've been hiding something from you guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.12,0:00:53.40,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,My name isn't Pecorine.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.43,0:00:58.20,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,It's Eustiana von Astraea.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.12,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I'm the princess of Landosol.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.72,0:01:03.67,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.26,0:01:08.58,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Yes, the one everyone calls "Her Majesty"
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.18,0:01:12.22,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,is named Eustiana, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.18,0:01:15.30,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I'm someone...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.34,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,everyone has forgotten about.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.18,0:01:25.15,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Including my parents.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.49,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Eustiana.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.25,0:01:36.11,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.58,0:01:37.73,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.30,0:01:40.83,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,The time has come at last.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.64,0:01:47.30,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,The world is vast.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.86,0:01:52.45,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Hear the voices of our people with your own ears,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.45,0:01:55.73,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,see what this nation is like with your own eyes,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.73,0:01:58.39,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,and experience what life has to offer it for yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.94,0:02:00.99,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Once you return from your journey,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.99,0:02:07.14,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,{\q2}you will have matured enough \Nto be a ruler worthy of ruling this nation.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.93,0:02:08.61,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.42,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Eustiana.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.32,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,This is a gift from me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.04,0:02:21.20,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\q2}This tiara is one of the royal accessories \Nhanded down in Landosol for generations.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.63,0:02:26.29,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It will surely keep you safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.67,0:02:32.81,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\q2}The only catch is that using \Nit will make you very hungry!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.82,0:02:40.01,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I look forward to it! I love to eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.83,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I'll be off now.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.64,0:03:06.87,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\t(712,2213,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Safe travels.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.01,0:03:13.46,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got to experience many great things
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.35,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,{\i1}while travelling around the continent of Astraea.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.17,0:03:21.80,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}But when I completed my journey \Nand returned to Landosol...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.56,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I, Eustiana has returned!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.19,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I wish to see my parents!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.92,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,Who do you think you're fooling?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.92,0:03:36.77,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,You dare utter {*}Princess Eustiana{*Eustiana-sama}'s name, you ruffian?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.99,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,H-Huh? What's happened to all of you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.99,0:03:42.71,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,It's me! Don't you recognise me?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.29,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.08,0:03:47.74,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,Get her!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.19,0:03:50.98,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.29,Default,Guard,0,0,0,,We have an intruder!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.30,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.13,0:04:06.45,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,You're Mother's meal attendant!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.76,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you again!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.87,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,It's me, Eustiana—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.57,0:04:19.45,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Does anyone remember me? Anyone?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.81,0:04:22.56,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,It's me! Eustiana!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.56,0:04:24.70,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Did everyone forget me?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.95,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Please, somebody!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.84,0:04:55.52,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I have returned from my journey.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.91,0:05:02.10,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I've heard the voices of our people with my own ears,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.83,0:05:06.78,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,and seen Landosol with my very own eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.86,0:05:19.38,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Does this mean I still haven't done enough,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.79,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Mother, Father?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.98,0:05:26.21,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.29,Default,Mother,0,0,0,,...might you be?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.95,0:05:40.61,Default,Kaiser,0,0,0,,I hear the squeaking of a little intruder,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.70,Default,Kaiser,0,0,0,,Mother, Father.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.33,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Ah, Eustiana!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.12,Default,Kaiser,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.38,0:05:58.59,Default,Kaiser,0,0,0,,I will exterminate this little rat for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.92,0:06:07.01,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,{\q2}I managed to escape from the person \Nwho had stolen my name,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.01,0:06:10.55,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,and set out on another journey.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.10,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,A journey without end.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.71,0:06:20.10,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,And that's when I met you, Yuuki{**-kun}, and {*}Karyl{*Kyaru-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.46,0:06:24.46,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I was so happy. Life was wonderful.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.14,0:06:26.83,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I met all of you,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.83,0:06:29.65,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,ate delicious meals...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.12,0:06:34.08,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,But I was always afraid.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.61,0:06:38.42,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Afraid that everyone would forget me again.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.03,0:06:44.72,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,{\q2}That the happier I felt, \Nthe more you'd distance yourselves from me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.80,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,If I'd told you the truth,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.80,0:06:54.59,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,that I was really Eustiana...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.72,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I was scared that...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.89,0:07:03.80,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's why.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.07,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why you would always
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.01,0:07:12.75,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,{\i1}hug the people important to you so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.32,0:07:16.95,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2\t(1823,3616,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}By doing that, you could clamp \Nall the connections you made together. {###}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.40,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,If only I had told the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.48,0:07:26.55,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I was so preoccupied with my own world.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.26,0:07:30.98,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,{\q2}And because I was stuck, \Nbecause of my selfishness...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.43,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I pushed {*}Karyl{*Kyaru-chan} away from me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.95,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,I won't leave you.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.66,0:07:47.98,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,{\q2}Whether you're {*}Princess Eustiana{*Eustiana-sama} \Nor {*}Lady Pecorine{*Pecorine-sama},
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.46,0:07:52.95,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,{\q2}the days we've spent together \Nas the Gourmet Guild
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.95,0:07:59.00,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,{\q2}form an invaluable bond \Nunlike any other treasure to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.73,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,I'm sure my lord feels the same way.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.89,0:08:07.32,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,And not just us, but {*}Lady Karyl{*Kyaru-sama} as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.49,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Is it okay if...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.15,0:08:25.38,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Is it okay if we stay like this for a little bit?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.28,0:08:50.43,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,Dumborine...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.92,0:09:12.90,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'd say those girls are figuring out \Nnew truths as well right about now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.70,0:09:19.99,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,Please trust me. I'm not your enemy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.75,0:09:25.97,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}Though, I guess I've dragged you in \Ntoo deep to be an ally.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.41,0:09:29.47,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,Well, have I ever.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.02,0:09:36.47,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,This space we're in is one I built.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.83,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,Does it look familiar?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.77,0:09:46.32,Default,Yuuki,0,0,0,,Ameth...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.97,0:09:52.33,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,That's right. She goes by "Ameth" now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.67,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,She's had your back through all this, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.55,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,She's so sweet.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.48,0:10:05.39,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}There are signs she's trying to slowly \Nand carefully restore your memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.74,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.86,0:10:20.92,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,This power is meant to protect your friends,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.92,0:10:24.88,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,but it's also capable of destroying you from within.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.31,0:10:29.72,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}At the moment you seem to have \Nlost most of your memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.31,0:10:34.70,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}Whether that's because of the Re:Dive \Nor not remains unclear.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.47,0:10:38.18,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, if you unleash this power as you are now,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.18,0:10:42.03,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}there's no telling how it would \Naffect your very existence itself.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.06,0:10:46.68,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,It probably influenced that earlier fight, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.13,0:10:51.80,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,Shadows attack people to consume their souls.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.79,0:10:55.19,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,They've already wiped out entire villages.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.67,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,And, more than likely,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.30,0:11:02.11,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,they showed up wherever you guys were
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.11,0:11:04.64,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,in search of more powerful souls.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.15,0:11:11.15,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,Those things don't just show up by accident.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.86,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}The will of something, or {\i1}someone{\i0}, \Nallows them to take shape.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.61,0:11:16.82,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,As long as you're trapped in this world,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.83,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,you can never escape that will.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.83,0:11:26.12,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}This world came to be as a result of \Nthe battle between you and that will.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.67,0:11:30.03,Default,Yuuki,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.17,0:11:33.55,Default,Yuuki,0,0,0,,These memories...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.27,0:11:44.18,Default,Charlie,0,0,0,,{*}Peco lady{*Peco-neesan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.78,Default,Ikacchi,0,0,0,,It's no use! I don't see her anyway!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.21,Default,Yasuko,0,0,0,,Quit your whining!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.11,0:11:52.02,Default,Yasuko,0,0,0,,I know she's gotta be a-okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.86,Default,Yasuko,0,0,0,,Get your butts into gear and find her!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.89,Default,Charlie,0,0,0,,But where could she be?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.89,0:11:58.04,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,Fall back!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.16,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,This place is still dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.16,0:12:02.95,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,All civilians, stand back!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.48,0:12:05.41,Default,Tomay,0,0,0,,It's Nightmare!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.77,0:12:07.15,Default,Ikacchi,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.12,Default,Ikacchi,0,0,0,,You always show up right when it's over!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.35,Default,Matsuri,0,0,0,,You don't have to put it like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.35,0:12:13.06,Default,Matsuri,0,0,0,,We're doing our best here!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.58,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,Stop that, Matsuri{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.58,0:12:17.84,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,{\q2}What good does it do to argue with \Nthe very civilians we are meant to protect?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.84,0:12:19.12,Default,Matsuri,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.60,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,She's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.10,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,We mustn't lose sight of our goal.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.29,0:12:25.22,Default,Matsuri,0,0,0,,Jun{**-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.18,0:12:29.70,Default,Ikacchi,0,0,0,,Aren't you... the captain of the palace knights?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.44,0:12:37.52,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.52,0:12:40.34,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Tomo, did you find anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.34,0:12:41.90,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,According to eyewitnesses,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.90,0:12:46.79,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,{\q2}there was a swordswoman who fought \Nthe monster to protect the townsfolk.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.71,0:12:52.33,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,{\q2}However, they say she abruptly \Nvanished along with the monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.05,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Vanished?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.05,0:12:54.88,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.42,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,As for the monster...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.60,0:13:04.10,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,{\q2}It shared many similarities with the \NShadows we've had trouble with recently.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.10,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.12,0:13:10.14,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,Wow, someone put on quite a show here.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.08,0:13:16.77,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,{\q2}Looks like it was even more powerful \Nthan the one I reported before.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.40,Default,Tomo,0,0,0,,Vice Captain...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.16,0:13:25.57,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,{\q2}A swordswoman who protected the people from \Na monster like that with no casualties, eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.45,0:13:31.42,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,{\q2}She interests me much more \Nthan these cretins{### I feel like there's a way better word to use here} do, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.42,0:13:36.67,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\q2}Chris{**-chan}, I respect how nonchalant you can be\N concerning other people's opinions about you,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.38,0:13:39.61,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,but I need you to focus on your job right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.61,0:13:42.34,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,My apologies, Captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.05,0:13:45.47,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,But doesn't this strike you as a little odd?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.87,0:13:49.44,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,A monster capable of doing this much damage
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.44,0:13:54.94,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,{\q2}found its way into Landosol, \Nthe royal capital of Astraea,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.94,0:14:00.68,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,{\q2}and yet we were none the wiser \Nuntil long after it had disappeared?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.80,0:14:09.08,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,What do you suppose His Majesty is thinking,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.08,0:14:12.02,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,deep in that castle of his?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.21,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Christina...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.84,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,Whoops. Don't mind me, just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.84,0:14:19.45,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,Pay it no mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.78,0:14:24.84,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,Oh, while I'm busy thinking out loud anyway...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.78,0:14:29.55,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,This is the kingdom of humans, Landosol,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.55,0:14:34.28,Default,Christina,0,0,0,,{\q2}so how and when did a beast \Nfind its way upon its throne, I wonder?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.28,0:14:43.52,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,Rising Tempest!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.29,0:14:54.75,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm getting in Her Majesty's way again.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.75,0:14:55.81,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.79,0:15:06.26,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}What do you want from me? \NHow am I supposed to choose?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.43,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, I want...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.50,0:15:23.29,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did I end up like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.09,0:15:27.70,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}I devoted my entire existence \Nto Her Majesty alone...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.31,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm helpless, aren't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.79,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really am utterly helpless.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.83,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.83,0:15:54.90,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,You were totally right. I {\i1}am{\i0} very selfish.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.90,0:15:56.27,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.37,0:16:01.36,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I want you to help me defeat that monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.43,0:16:05.19,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,Moron.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.44,0:16:20.70,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.42,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}I know I threw a lot at you \Nin such a short amount of time.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.23,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,But it's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.23,0:16:31.22,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}All of us in Labyrinth \Nwill protect you and your friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.79,0:16:33.71,Default,Yuuki,0,0,0,,I'll protect them.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.44,Default,Yuuki,0,0,0,,I'll protect my friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.08,0:16:53.08,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}I took such a long way around \Nto finally see you in person,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.74,0:16:55.52,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,and it looks like it was well worth it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.11,0:16:59.33,Default,Shizuru,0,0,0,,Master, we can't hold out much longer!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.18,0:17:02.83,Default,Rino,0,0,0,,Our brother's friends are in trouble!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.11,0:17:05.00,Default,Shizuru,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.00,0:17:08.60,Default,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\q2}Should we jump in and help them, even if \Nthat means we give ourselves away to the enemy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.60,0:17:12.32,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}No need, it looks like all the pieces \Nhave finally fallen into place.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.69,0:17:16.84,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,And with that, let's do this!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.12,0:17:31.53,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,This is my power,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.91,0:17:33.87,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,Object Transformation.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.95,0:17:48.42,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'll lend you just a bit of it \Nso you can move forward.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.20,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,I have faith that the bonds you build
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.20,0:17:57.05,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,will save all of them from this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.72,0:18:03.69,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Yuuki{**-kun}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.69,0:18:04.60,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.10,0:18:06.48,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.28,Default,Yuuki,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.41,0:18:17.53,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,This power...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.73,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,My magic power...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.42,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,My lord's feelings...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.25,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,May the light's blessing be with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.10,0:18:49.61,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Princess Strike!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.44,0:19:00.46,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,I hope you're ready for this!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.46,0:19:02.92,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,Grim Burst!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.81,0:19:18.43,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,Grant my lord a body of steel.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.29,0:19:22.18,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,Grant my lord the speed of a falcon.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.93,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,Now, let us advance!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.91,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,To victory!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.77,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,Excellent swordsmanship,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.77,0:20:05.94,Default,Labyrista,0,0,0,,my Princess Knight.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.24,Default,Yasuko,0,0,0,,Quit crying, you nincompoops!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.24,Default,Charlie,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.39,Default,Ikacchi,0,0,0,,If {*}Peco lady{*Peco-neesan} and her friends are gone...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.92,Default,Yasuko,0,0,0,,Don't even {\i1}think{\i0} about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.04,Default,Ikacchi,0,0,0,,But, Mama...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.86,Default,Yasuko,0,0,0,,{\q2}If you've got the time to cry, \Nget your butt to work!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.53,0:20:36.70,Default,Yasuko,0,0,0,,Also, that's "Mom" to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.59,Default,Charlie,0,0,0,,{*}Peco lady{*Peco-neesan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.31,Default,Ikacchi,0,0,0,,You're okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.06,0:21:10.02,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,{*}Karyl{*Kyaru}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.16,0:21:16.21,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Thank you for honouring my selfish request.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.93,0:21:23.97,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,That was the last time, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.73,0:21:26.56,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.23,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,I love you, {*}Karyl{*Kyaru-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.19,0:22:52.42,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,Bread really is best with runny eggs!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.42,0:22:53.64,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,It sure is!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.64,0:22:56.29,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,It makes me feel the joy of a fresh morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.52,0:23:02.44,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,Your appetite has grown quite healthy, my lord.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.99,0:23:05.70,Default,Kokkoro,0,0,0,,I'm beyond delighted.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.70,0:23:06.92,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.92,0:23:10.70,Default,Karyl,0,0,0,,{\q2}He's no longer the little beansprout \Nhe was when we first met.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.07,0:23:12.58,Default,Yuuki,0,0,0,,Mhm!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.94,0:23:16.08,Default,Yuuki,0,0,0,,What's the plan today?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.72,0:23:17.86,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,That's easy!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.47,0:23:20.96,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,What's the goal of the Gourmet Guild?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.02,0:23:24.85,Default,All,0,0,0,,The study of all the delicious food in this world!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.85,0:23:25.82,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.36,0:23:36.56,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,It's time to set off.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.56,0:23:38.86,Default,Pecorine,0,0,0,,Onto our next adventure!
